org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.utils

Class RMStatistics

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.utils.RMStatistics

  • public final class RMStatistics
extends Object
    This class represents the statistics of the Resource Manager. Different kind of values are collected by interpreting incoming events from the Resource Manager.
    Since:
    ProActive Scheduling 1.1
